  <trk>
    <name>Sentier des Chamois</name>
    <desc>The Chamois Path runs through the Haut Val de Bagnes nature reserve. Along steep paths high above the valley floor, you will enjoy breathtaking views and numerous opportunities to observe wildlife.</desc>
